title: Tin Foil Hat #47: The Mandela Effect with Detective 47
description:
Welcome to the 47th episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode Ryan and Sam welcome musician extraordinaire Detective 47 to the show. On this episode we discuss...
1) the Nov 8th Higherside Chats Swapcast live at the La Jolla Comedy Store with Eddie Bravo and Greg Carlwood!
2) The new Tin Foil Hat Patreon..... Patreon.com/TinFoilHat
2)the Man behind the Tin Foil Hat Intro
3) The Mandela Effect
4)Cern Theories
5) Psychedelics
6) The Monitor Head Video
You can find Detective 47 all over the internet at
Instagram/detective47/
www.whoisdetective47.com
http://detective47.bandcamp.com/releases
The Star Spangled Banner Video by Detective 47
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2j4CVhN0vj0&feature=youtu.be
Thank you so much for all of your support!
